        </mc-text>
        <mc-spacer class="h-[12px]" />
        <mc-text class="text-center text-[36px] font-bold text-[#ffffff] leading-[44px]">
          Future Tech Summit 2026
        </mc-text>
        <mc-spacer class="h-[16px]" />
        <mc-text class="text-center text-[16px] text-[#c0c0c0] leading-[24px]">
